# Optional local development safety mode (ignored by production builds):
# ordinary `npm run dev` keeps the existing lead-write behavior. Set this to
# "true" when you deliberately want forms to validate and complete without a
# network request or saved lead. The Partner Demo launcher enforces this itself.
# VITE_DEMO_LEAD_MODE=true
